  "instructions": [
    "Mash avocado in a bowl with half of the lime juice and set aside.",
    "Mix jalapenos, onion, tomato, cilantro, remaining lime juice, garlic, cayenne pepper (if using), and salt into the mashed avocado mixture until well combined.",
